Ngwana wa Taung ke masalela a leraga la ngwana o monnye a bontshwa jaaka sekai sa motho wa moAforika. Le fihletswe ka 1924 ke babereki ba berekela Northern Lime Company ko [[Taung]], [[Aforika Borwa]]. Raymond Dart o ehlalosa are ke sebopego se seswa mo dibukeng tsa Nature ka 1925.

